<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Submission Processing Error</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .header {
      color: #005ea2;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">ECMPS Submission Error Notification</div>
<div class="content">
  <p>Dear User,</p>
  <p>
    We regret to inform you that an error occurred while processing your submission for <strong>{{configuration}}</strong> (Submission ID: <strong>{{submissionId}}</strong>).
  </p>
  <p>
    Please contact ECMPS support at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> for assistance. Provide the Error Reference ID below when contacting support.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Error Reference ID:</strong> {{errorId}}
  </p>
  <p>Thank you for your patience.</p>
  <p>Sincerely,</p>
  <p>ECMPS Support Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
